---
---

<section class="why-section">
  <div class="why-inner">
    <header class="why-head">
      <span class="why-eyebrow">Hvorfor vælge Siite?</span>
      <h2 class="why-title">Vi leverer mere end<br>bare en hjemmeside</h2>
    </header>

    <div class="why-grid">
      <article class="why-card">
        <span class="why-num">01</span>
        <span class="why-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-handshake-angle"></i></span>
        <h3>Én partner — ikke fem leverandører</h3>
        <p>Web, SEO, Google Ads, Meta, content og strategi samlet ét sted. Det betyder sammenhæng, fart i beslutningerne og ingen tabte bolde mellem systemer, bureauer og leverandører.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="why-card">
        <span class="why-num">02</span>
        <span class="why-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-chart-simple"></i></span>
        <h3>Resultater før alt andet</h3>
        <p>Vi bygger løsninger, der kan måles på bundlinjen – ikke bare buzzwords og flotte præsentationer. Performance, leads og omsætning er hvad vi leverer og står inde for.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="why-card">
        <span class="why-num">03</span>
        <span class="why-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-user-shield"></i></span>
        <h3>Fast rådgiver — ejerskab hele vejen</h3>
        <p>Du har én fast rådgiver gennem hele forløbet, som kender din forretning, dine mål og dine tal. Vi tager ansvar fra start til slut og står på mål for det, der bliver leveret.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .why-section {
    background: #ffffff;
    padding: 140px 48px 160px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  /* Blød orange glød i baggrunden */
  .why-section::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -180px;
    right: -120px;
    width: 460px;
    height: 460px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(240, 90, 36, 0.12), transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .why-inner {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .why-head {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 72px;
  }

  .why-eyebrow {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: 'Comfortaa', cursive;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #f05a24;
    margin-bottom: 22px;
    padding: 7px 18px;
    border: 1.5px solid #f9ddd2;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: #fff7f3;
  }

  .why-title {
    font-family: 'Comfortaa', cursive;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.4rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.14;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
  }

  .why-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 28px;
  }

  .why-card {
    position: relative;
    background: #fbfbfb;
    border: 1px solid #efefef;
    border-radius: 24px;
    padding: 44px 36px 40px;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease, border-color 0.3s ease;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .why-card::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    height: 4px;
    width: 100%;
    background: #f05a24;
    transform: scaleX(0);
    transform-origin: left;
    transition: transform 0.35s ease;
  }

  .why-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-8px);
    box-shadow: 0 26px 60px rgba(240, 90, 36, 0.13);
    border-color: #f9ddd2;
  }

  .why-card:hover::after {
    transform: scaleX(1);
  }

  .why-num {
    position: absolute;
    top: 28px;
    right: 34px;
    font-family: 'Comfortaa', cursive;
    font-size: 2.4rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #f3f3f3;
    line-height: 1;
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .why-card:hover .why-num {
    color: #fde4d9;
  }

  .why-icon {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 60px;
    height: 60px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    background: #fff3ee;
    color: #f05a24;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    transition: background 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .why-card:hover .why-icon {
    background: #f05a24;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .why-card h3 {
    font-family: 'Comfortaa', cursive;
    font-size: 1.18rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    max-width: 90%;
  }

  .why-card p {
    font-family: 'Comfortaa', cursive;
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #777;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .why-section {
      padding: 90px 24px 100px;
    }

    .why-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .why-head {
      margin-bottom: 48px;
    }
  }
</style>

<script>
  import { gsap } from "gsap";
  import { ScrollTrigger } from "gsap/ScrollTrigger";

  gsap.registerPlugin(ScrollTrigger);

  gsap.from(".why-head > *", {
    y: 28,
    opacity: 0,
    duration: 0.8,
    ease: "power3.out",
    stagger: 0.12,
    scrollTrigger: {
      trigger: ".why-head",
      start: "top 80%",
      once: true,
    },
  });

  gsap.from(".why-card", {
    y: 48,
    opacity: 0,
    duration: 0.8,
    ease: "power3.out",
    stagger: 0.14,
    scrollTrigger: {
      trigger: ".why-grid",
      start: "top 78%",
      once: true,
    },
  });
</script>
